<text>The Times is a British daily newspaper based in London, the original English-language newspaper titled &quot;Times&quot;.

The Times may also refer to:

== Newspapers ==
* &quot;The Times&quot; (South Africa)
* &quot;The Times&quot; (Victor Harbor), a regional newspaper in South Australia
* &quot;The Times of Ceylon&quot;
* &quot;The Times of India&quot;
* &quot;The Times of Israel&quot;
* &quot;Times of Malta&quot;

=== United States ===
